Key Features:

No server storage: Messages go directly between browsers via WebRTC
Basic encryption: Simple XOR encryption for message content
No dependencies: Pure HTML/CSS/JavaScript - works in all modern browsers
No logging: Impossible to log what the server never sees
Ephemeral: Messages exist only during the session

How it works:

Each user gets a unique session ID
Share your ID with someone to connect
Messages are encrypted and sent directly browser-to-browser
No messages are stored anywhere - they disappear when you disconnect

Browser Support:

Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge (all modern versions)
Mobile browsers supported
No plugins or downloads required
